{"tid":2491263,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"輝瑞：武肺病毒不斷變異 須一年內要打加強針 或要每年打針維持保護","createTime":"2021-04-16T07:40:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-16T07:47:26.000Z","uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4e0b2349bece8b23f80ea1cc52f7e6ab6402392f","tid":2491263,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T07:40:01.000Z","msg":"輝瑞：接種一年內要打加強針 或要每年打針維持保護<br />\n<br />\n藥廠「輝瑞」行政總裁布拉表示，民眾打完新冠疫苗後一年內，可能要再打多一針「加強針」，然後每年都要再打疫苗，從而在新冠病毒不斷變異的情況下，維持預防能力。他說，尚要進行更多研究，了解是否有必要每年都打針。<br />\n<br />\n「輝瑞」本身同「BioNTech」合作研發新冠疫苗，本港都有購入<span class=\"gold\">同類疫苗</span>。布拉舉例指，部份疫苗只要打一針就得，包括預防小兒麻痹症的脊髓灰質炎疫苗，不過預防流感的疫苗就要「年年打」，而新冠病毒看起來更似流感病毒。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/international/2387491\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Finternational%2F2387491&d=oTLiiFgDV%2FfsDwDkP3XzLS%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=7dae7fa3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/international/2387491</a>"},{"pid":"3426b332e280846d22c608357d8f9695c44ddea4","tid":2491263,"uid":137038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T07:41:38.000Z","msg":"弱感冒都想呃人年年交保護費 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a6b510dd1751d3700ebcd8fadd9fc1bdae7e05b","tid":2491263,"uid":276865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T07:42:58.000Z","msg":"可能, 或, 標題就改做須<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c62d1bd6c8cb75e1c8f8cfd2a6433fedd27cc9ae","tid":2491263,"uid":54431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T07:47:26.000Z","msg":"究竟係人類滅絕<br />\n定還是疫苗商家想借機撈一筆先拖慢黎打"}]}